videos.description: Oregon's Sabrina Ionescu shows off his passing vision, sending a backdoor pass that leads Satou Sabally to the basket for an easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Ionescu delivers beautiful backdoor pass to Sabally) 2020/03/01 ESHEET

videos.headline: Ionescu delivers beautiful backdoor pass to Sabally

videos.description: Ruthy Hebard pokes the ball loose and dives to the floor to gain possession, then passes ahead to Taylor Chavez for the layup in transition.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Oregon's Hebard dishes assist from the floor) 2020/03/01 ESHEET
